Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:42.36,EngED,,0,0,0,,I seek the solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:49.28,KarED,,0,0,0,,{\k71}ko{\k52}ku{\k55}no {\k50}na{\k93}ka {\k49}mo{\k55}to {\k213}mu
