Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:15.10,EngED,,0,0,0,,Ah...the words of prayer tremble...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:22.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嗚呼 弱きいのちが消えても
