Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:22.32,EngED,,0,0,0,,Ah even if the faint-hearted\N were to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:30.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くりかえす 輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:30.20,KarED,,0,0,0,,{\k80}ku{\k24}ri{\k55}ka{\k28}e{\k67}su {\k70}inn{\k27}en {\k24}no {\k29}na{\k51}ga{\k98}re {\k50}ta{\k50}do{\k54}ri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:30.20,EngED,,0,0,0,,Following the recurring paths of fate.
