Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:38.96,EngED,,0,0,0,,I gaze upon the never-ending world's destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くりかえし 詠われる者達よ
